caption: Sophie Vortex storms the neon-lit bar of downtown NeoCity, her silhouette slicing through rain-soaked streets as she sips on a synth cocktail. Her confident stride and electric glow light up the night, revealing a body that commands attention and a mind that writes its own story. The scene is lit by neon, rain, and the pulse of the city, as if it were a post from a stylish rebel documenting her night in a dystopian city ⚡💫 #cyberpunk #futurism #streetfashion #digitalart #neonaesthetics
